== Theoretical context (psion-ontology framing) ==

In the [[Psi_Field|ψ-field]] Lagrangian picture, a defensive
configuration that decouples a region from psionic perturbation is one
that '''suppresses the EM field-strength scalar
<math>F^2</math>''' inside the region - the source term for
[[Psion|psion]] production via the
<math>\alpha\,\psi\,F_{\mu\nu}F^{\mu\nu}</math> vertex. Conventional
[[Faraday cage]] / shielding hardware partially achieves this for the
direct ([[CEMI Field Theory|cemi]], <math>g_F\,C\,F^2</math>) channel;
the indirect channel additionally requires suppression of the
displacement-current pattern (see the
[[HelmKit_Architecture#Both-channel_sham_requirement|both-channel
sham]] requirement). The Mk-level engineering above is unchanged by
this framing.


